00:35:19.730 --> 00:35:22.730
But it's really just talking
about the force with respect

00:35:22.730 --> 00:35:24.210
to a distance.

00:35:24.210 --> 00:35:27.230
It's not telling us
anything about what happens

00:35:27.230 --> 00:35:29.520
